title: Dark Reign - The List (Marvel|2009|Digital-HR|Minutemen)
description:
Overview:   Norman Osborn plans on making a list, checking it twice, and delivering
            an unhealthy amount of Dark Reign madness directly into the lives of 
            super heroes both naughty and nice in Dark Reign: The List, a series of 
            eight interconnected stories heralding the next major chapter in the 
            Marvel Universe's current saga.

Contains:   Dark Reign - The List - Amazing Spider-Man 01 (2009) (digital) 
            (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
            Dark Reign - The List - Avengers 01 (2009) (digital) 
            (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
            Dark Reign - The List - Daredevil 01 (2009) (digital) 
            (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
            Dark Reign - The List - Hulk 01 (2009) (digital) (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
            Dark Reign - The List - Punisher 01 (2009) (digital) 
            (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
            Dark Reign - The List - Secret Warriors 01 (2009) (digital) 
            (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
            Dark Reign - The List - Wolverine 01 (2009) (digital) 
            (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
            Dark Reign - The List - X-Men 01 (2009) (digital) (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
